Package fr.epita.iam.business Description

Provides the classes necessary to implement the different business features of the application.

Each business feature has been placed in ins own class to allow for future changes without necessarily affecting other features/classes. These include:

Creating and Identity

Deleting an identity

Updating an identity

Hot Chocolate
